		<td><b>Issue with &quot;Mark forums read&quot;</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just a minor issue with the &quot;Mark forums read&quot; feature: It only works until the next time you log in. I click the &quot;Mark forums read&quot; button, and it works fine. But when I come back the next day, all the forum icons are unread again. This even happens if there have been no new posts in those forums, which can get rather annoying. I would like to see this fixed, if possible.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


